thread.title: BRIEF-MLP FY Net Profit Up At EUR 27.8 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-MLP FY Net Profit Up At EUR 27.8 Mln
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - MLP SE:
* FY OPERATING EBIT ROSE 33 PERCENT TO 46.7 MILLION EUR * FY REVENUE ROSE 3 PERCENT TO 628.2 MILLION EUR * FY TOTAL REVENUE UP 3 PERCENT TO EUR 628.2 MILLION (EUR 610.4 MILLION)
* ‍EBIT IS EXPECTED TO REMAIN AT LEVEL OF OPERATING EBIT RECORDED IN 2017 (EUR 46.7 MILLION)​
* FY NET PROFIT INCREASED TO EUR 27.8 MILLION * ‍INCREASING DIVIDEND FROM 8 CENTS TO 20 CENTS PER SHARE​ * FY COMMISSION INCOME INCREASED FROM EUR 570.1 MILLION TO EUR 589.9 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
